name: proto-service
description: ### How to install: - Make sure "protobuf" has been installed on your machine. [link](https://github.com/golang/protobuf) - Run:     `go get google.golang.org/grpc/cmd/protoc-gen-go-grpc`     `go install google.golang.org/grpc/cmd/protoc-gen-go-grpc` - See [link](https://github.com/grpc/grpc-web) to install protoc-gen-grpc-web
